Q3:

The Rise of Agentic AI: A New Era of Intelligent Collaboration:

Answer:

Automated and intelligent agents or applications are made by humans which can done multiple tasks for humans like switch off/on lights, cooking, etc. these agents can be one and multiples and through machine learning and natural language processing will be interact with each other also with humans and will enhance productivity and innovation. Agents can work independently to achieve their specific tasks and can work on colloboration environment by sharing information and their specific knowledge. Agents will learn and adapt new techniqes and information. they are scalable which means if there is load they can increase more agents to handle work load pressure.